---
source: tests/degraded_honesty.rs
assertion: demo run executes safe manifests with audit-ledger rows and evidence artifacts
schema:
  list: ee.demo.list.v1
  run: ee.demo.run.v1
  run_plan: ee.demo.run_plan.v1
  show: ee.demo.show.v1
  verify: ee.demo.verify.v1
contracts:
  - demo list reads manifest entries without durable mutation
  - demo run --dry-run returns an execution plan without running commands
  - demo run executes safe manifest commands and records stdout, stderr, metadata, and audit evidence
  - demo run aborts remaining steps after the first failure unless continue-on-error is requested
  - demo run rejects unsafe shell commands before execution
  - demo show reads persisted audit-ledger rows for the selected demo
  - demo verify checks declared evidence artifacts and rejects symlink evidence
  - demo verify reports missing or optional artifacts without fabricating success
evidence:
  - data.demos[].id
  - data.demos[].status
  - data.demos[].commands[].executed
  - data.demos[].commands[].exitCode
  - data.demos[].commands[].auditId
  - data.demos[].commands[].evidenceDir
  - data.demos[].commands[].artifacts
  - data.firstFailure
  - data.auditEntries
  - data.artifactResults
  - tests.fixtures.golden.demo.release_context_demo
